      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just so tired of fighting. like every single day is a battle just to exist as myself and it feels like the world is just constantly pushing back. idk if i have anything left in me to keep trying to change things or even just to keep going like this. it just feels heavy. too heavy.",
